  "desc": "<p>香菱的助手兼搭档。</p>",
  "iconUrl": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/06/26/47826599/aed6d782110b4a976ecc5deffddd9bff_4935961229931532261.png",
